{
  "dashboard": {
    "title": "ðŸ¤– System Health - SIMPLE AND CLEAR",
    "tags": ["human", "simple", "health"],
    "panels": [
      {
        "title": "ðŸ’š OVERALL SYSTEM STATUS",
        "type": "text",
        "content": "# ðŸŽ¯ QUICK DIAGNOSTICS\n\n## âœ… WHAT'S GOOD:\n- System running stable\n- All services available\n- Memory within limits\n- CPU not overloaded\n\n## âš ï¸ NEED ATTENTION:\n- Network load\n- Free disk space\n- Error count in logs\n\n## ðŸš¨ ALERT SIGNALS:\n- Memory > 85% - need cleanup\n- CPU > 80% - check for leaks\n- Disk > 90% - urgent cleanup\n- Errors > 5% - check code",
        "gridPos": {"h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0}
      },
      {
        "title": "ðŸ§  MEMORY - SIMPLE EXPLANATION",
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [{
          "expr": "(1 - (node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes / node_memory_MemTotal_bytes)) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Memory used"
        }],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 70, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 85, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 10}
      },
      {
        "title": "âš¡ CPU - PROCESSOR LOAD",
        "type": "stat", 
        "targets": [{
          "expr": "100 - (avg by (instance) (rate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"}[5m])) * 100)",
          "legendFormat": "CPU load"
        }],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 50, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 80, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 10}
      },
      {
        "title": "ðŸ’¾ DISK - FREE SPACE",
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [{
          "expr": "(1 - (node_filesystem_avail_bytes / node_filesystem_size_bytes)) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Disk space used"
        }],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent", 
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 80, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 90, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 10}
      },
      {
        "title": "ðŸ“± OUR APPLICATION - ACTIVITY",
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [{
          "expr": "sum(rate(app_requests_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Requests per second"
        }],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "reqps",
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "blue"},
                {"value": 1, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 5, "color": "yellow"}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 10}
      }
    ],
    "time": {"from": "now-1h", "to": "now"},
    "refresh": "10s"
  },
  "overwrite": true
}